ieurs années dans les banlieues de la région métropolitaine de Montréal.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aLocal transitzQuébec (Province)zMontréal. 0aTransportationzQuébec (Province)zMontréal. 7aARCHITECTURE / Urban & Land Use Planning.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311127221408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2021z978311127464540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9782763756417?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763756417423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763756417/original  a978-3-11-127221-4  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-127464-5  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2021b2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles